			<h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin: 0;">About This Plugin</h3>
		</div>
		<p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75; color: #475569; margin: 0 0 14px;">
			The <strong>Editorial Board ORCID Verification</strong> plugin brings authenticated identity management to your journal's editorial board. It integrates directly with the ORCID registry to verify board members, manage consent workflows, and protect against unauthorized listings.
		</p>
		<p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75; color: #475569; margin: 0;">
			Designed for journals that prioritize <strong>transparency</strong> and <strong>research integrity</strong>, this plugin ensures every editorial board member is who they claim to be — verified through their institutional ORCID iD.
		</p>
	</div>

